title: Suzanne Collins The Underland Chronicles
description: I have put the whole series on to one .m4b file.  I like to listen to book series this way so I do not have to switch over to the next book in the series.  iTunes will not play a .m4b file larger than 3.99 GB in size to the end,so you have brake up larger series in to blocks.  iTunes saves your place in the audiobook , if you use .m4b files.  I ripped the this whole series from CD's I got from the library.  I have listened to the entire file, it sounds great.  The file can not be split. If, you do not like the torrent the way I have done it,do not download it or seed it.
